{"tid":110544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［心事］如果有一日阿媽再無煩你...","createTime":"2017-02-06T17:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T01:53:48.000Z","uid":75211,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbd9f641f464d381cf2d4b7cc0620742a3c1c05","tid":110544,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"阿媽最近老左好多<br />\n係咁生白頭髮出黎<br />\n皮膚皺紋越黎越多<br />\n個人成日癡癡呆呆好似無精神咁<br />\n成日出街硬係有野唔記得帶<br />\n成日都話呢到痛個度痛好似成日整親咁<br />\n以前佢成日係屋企問野問黎問去吵吵鬧鬧<br />\n但呢排開始好小聽到佢既吵鬧聲同問長問短<br />\n唔知點解最緊個心凝住凝住有一日無咗阿媽會點<br />\n越諗就越想喊，每次到呢個時候就會諗一次呢個畫面<br />\n細個我阿媽就同咗老豆離咗婚 我阿媽一手一腳嗅大我<br />\n有無巴絲同我一樣咁諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e9ae1db853b2388124d6423507dd5588c5e067","tid":110544,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"加油 我同你情況差唔多 好明你感受 盡量唔好令佢難過 多d 陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  share 下正能量比你"},{"pid":"822dd6375e9693b63063df808c5df9d95fa0e636","tid":110544,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46f663f6e284abaad2b56653e40768000ec7ae8","tid":110544,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚嗰日既來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea615225cefe7bc63bca792ccbe37f871aeee54","tid":110544,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油 我同你情況差唔多 好明你感受 盡量唔好令佢難過 多d 陪佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  share 下正能量比你</blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk